    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Twelve years later, history is rhyming. Democrats were vaulted into office on popular promises to tax the wealthy, but they are now generating national headlines about their proposal to provide new tax breaks narrowly targeted to enrich their affluent blue-state donors, just as a"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            5
          ],
          1,
          " new survey"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " shows nearly two thirds of Americans see the party as “out of touch with the concerns of most people.” And now the Republican machine is already gearing up to demagogue the issue in 2022."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
