          "abandoned a $15 minimum wage"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ", Democratic leaders are pushing a regressive proposal to allow wealthy property owners to deduct more of their their state and local taxes (SALT) from their federal taxes."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "This initiative, which would provide almost no benefit to the working class, isn’t some small tweak. After Democrats gutted their wildly popular initiatives to expand Medicare and lower drug prices, the tax initiative has now become "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            10
          ],
          1,
          "one of the most expensive"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " provisions in the entire Build Back Better legislation."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "The whole initiative seems deliberately sculpted to hand the American Right a weapon to bludgeon Democrats ahead of the election. Indeed, you can imagine it being Fox News’ "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            11
          ],
          1,
          "latest"
